properties.Name: CollectionLetterType
properties.Description:
A classification of Collection Letters based upon common characteristics or functions performed.

Examples:
-  Reminder
-  30 Days Overdue
-  60 Days Overdue
-  Plan to refer to third-party collection service
-  Referral to third-party collection service
-  Legal action will result
-  Legal action has been initiated
